Package org.howard.edu.lsp.assignment4

Class IntegerSet

java.lang.Object
org.howard.edu.lsp.assignment4.IntegerSet
public class IntegerSet extends Object
This class implements a mathematical set of Integer. Stored values ate unique. Internally values are maintained in sorted order as that makes insert, delete, lookup and set level operations far cheaper algorithmically.
Since:
0.1

    • IntegerSet

      public IntegerSet(ArrayList<Integer> set)
      Constructor to construct this collection using am ArrayList of values. NOTE: As there is no guarantee that the parameter set has unique values the list is filtered and duplicate values removed.
      Parameters:
      set - is am array list containing data to be imported into this IntegerSet.
